ygData.messageBody:
At 9sp per month? You think your cash matters?

You are welcome to play the game anyway you like. Why bother posting here?
Takes time from your levels. I been looking all over but so far can't find
any merchants that sell either honor nor respect. Guess those are quest
items you have to actually earn from the other players.

I hope you get to 48th really, really fast! We long for the day you spam
the list with your ad to sell your char on ebay. Maybe we should take up a
collection right now? How much for your account?

Sylly
Bard of the 11th level
HogCallers Inn
Freeport, Innoruuk
